LogicalColumn.name: Avg. Revenue per Sale to Individuals

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."# of Contacts with Orders" > 0 THEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."Total Order Revenue" / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."# of Contacts with Orders" ELSE 0 END

LogicalColumn.name: ROI %

LogicalColumn.name: 5 Year Cost Ratio with GiftAid
LogicalColumn.Description: This metric calculates the cost ratio of COG campaigns based on a modelled 5 year future value with gift aid. This metric is used to more accuraretly predict the inital cost ratio of a COG campaign rather than using individual donations. ( Marketing Costs / (if Gift aid = Y then 5 Year COG value * (1+gift Aid) else 5 Year COG value)

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)" / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."5 Year Cog Income (Gift Aid)"

LogicalColumn.name: 12 month COG ROI % With GiftAid
LogicalColumn.Description: This metric calculates the ROI of a campaign based on an estimated 12 month COG value with gift aid (IF Giftaid = 'Y' then 12 month COG value * 1+(Gift Aid) ELSE 12 month COG value)

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)" > 0 THEN 100 * ("Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."12 Month COG Revenue with GiftAid" - "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)") / "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)" ELSE 0 END

LogicalColumn.name: 5 Year Cost Ratio (No Gift Aid)
LogicalColumn.Description: This metric calculates the cost ratio of COG campaigns based on a modelled 5 year future value. This metric is used to more accuraretly predict the inital cost ratio of a COG campaign rather than using individual donations. ( Marketing Costs / 5 Year COG value )

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: "Core"."Fact Compound - Marketing Goals Achieved"."Actual Expenses" / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."5 Year Cog Income (No Gift Aid)"

LogicalColumn.name: 5 Year COG ROI % with GiftAid
LogicalColumn.Description: This metric calculates the ROI % of COG campaigns based on a modelled 5 year future value including Gift Aid. This metric is used to more accuraretly predict the inital cost ratio of a COG campaign rather than using individual donations. (100*(if Gift aid = Y then 5 Year COG value * (1+gift Aid) else 5 Year COG value) / Marketing Costs

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)" > 0 THEN 100 * ("Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."5 Year Cog Income (Gift Aid)" - "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)") / "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)" ELSE 0 END

LogicalColumn.name: Cost/Income Ratio inc. Potential Gift Aid Amount
LogicalColumn.Description: This is the ratio of the Cost of a campaign vs. the income, including Potential Gift Aid regardless of whether it has been claimed.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: "Core"."Fact - Marketing - Cost"."Marketing Cost (Actual)" / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Payment"."Potential Amount with Gift Aid"
